parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield wiper motor can cause the wipers to stop working or work intermittently, reducing visibility and increasing the risk of accidents, especially during inclement weather.
symptoms: Windshield wipers stop working or work intermittently
wipers come on and off on their own
wipers only work when the modulator is wiggled
wipers work only at high speeds and stop at low speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat frame can cause the seat to recline or collapse, leading to loss of control of the vehicle, increased risk of injury, and potentially fatal accidents.
symptoms: The seat reclines or collapses unexpectedly
the seat frame cracks or breaks
the seat becomes loose or unstable
the driver loses control of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake light switch can cause the brake lights to malfunction, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially when using cruise control. This can also lead to unintended acceleration, loss of control, and increased stopping distances.
symptoms: Intermittent or complete failure of brake lights
cruise control not disengaging when brakes are applied
vehicle continues to accelerate when brakes are applied
brake lights do not illuminate when brakes are applied.
